<s>Resting stages are not known.</s><s>Chemo-organotrophs.</s><s>Strict aerobes.</s><s>Require seawater for growth.</s><s>The major respiratory quinone is MK-7.</s><s>The major cellular fatty acids are 16 : 1 and 15 : 0.</s><s>This genus belongs to the family ‘<em>Flammeovirgaceae</em>’, phylum <em>Bacteroidetes</em>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Rapidithrix thailandica</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>